title: Call to Artists and Youth to "Create Community Colour" (City of Victoria)
text: ( Source : City of Victoria ) October 21 , 2015 A new initiative aims to beautify six graffiti hotspots downtown and in Victoria neighbourhoods with 10 colourful murals produced by professional artists in collaboration with local youth. Local
